  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/465c0f91069c84d7ade63527445fe7a1.avif?t=1698083574\" width=620 height=182 /></span><br><br>EndZ Village is a 2D post-apocalyptic zombie survival game developed by DEVCLIED. This 2D survival game immerses you in a post-apocalyptic world infested with zombies, where humanity is fighting endlessly against the constant onslaught of infected zombie hordes.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/e88a6197930ce8ef81c8a4dbf7d1ea5f.poster.avif?t=1698083574\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/e88a6197930ce8ef81c8a4dbf7d1ea5f.webm?t=1698083574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/e88a6197930ce8ef81c8a4dbf7d1ea5f.mp4?t=1698083574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build a strong village to fight against the zombies. Manage your village's resources and construction. Find ways to prevent your village's destruction. Unexpected apocalyptic events may occur during gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/b40ca8362274f2a20d6737a6f623d1eb.poster.avif?t=1698083574\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/b40ca8362274f2a20d6737a6f623d1eb.webm?t=1698083574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/b40ca8362274f2a20d6737a6f623d1eb.mp4?t=1698083574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Treacherous factions of zombies, hidden resources and untold stories are waiting to be discovered. Remember to stay vigilant for the sake of your village or risk being consumed by the untold horrors that await in EndZ Village.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/9d17c5b99957a71f612e17cbab5934d6.avif?t=1698083574\" width=620 height=182 /></span><br><br>-Zombie Age simulation<br>-Village construction<br>-Real-time survival engine<br>-Multiple types of zombies<br>-Variety of weapons to build and use<br>-Beautiful 2D graphics and animation<br><br>-Prevent attacks from zombies during village development<br>-Build weapons to increase attack power and defense<br>-Manage resources with farming<br>-Search for resources<br>-Produce meat with animal husbandry<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/6ca06cdfa6fdcdb4a50551bb235821c6.avif?t=1698083574\" width=620 height=280 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/465c0f91069c84d7ade63527445fe7a1.avif?t=1698083574\" width=620 height=182 /></span><br><br>EndZ Village is a 2D post-apocalyptic zombie survival game developed by DEVCLIED. This 2D survival game immerses you in a post-apocalyptic world infested with zombies, where humanity is fighting endlessly against the constant onslaught of infected zombie hordes.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/e88a6197930ce8ef81c8a4dbf7d1ea5f.poster.avif?t=1698083574\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/e88a6197930ce8ef81c8a4dbf7d1ea5f.webm?t=1698083574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/e88a6197930ce8ef81c8a4dbf7d1ea5f.mp4?t=1698083574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build a strong village to fight against the zombies. Manage your village's resources and construction. Find ways to prevent your village's destruction. Unexpected apocalyptic events may occur during gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/b40ca8362274f2a20d6737a6f623d1eb.poster.avif?t=1698083574\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/b40ca8362274f2a20d6737a6f623d1eb.webm?t=1698083574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/b40ca8362274f2a20d6737a6f623d1eb.mp4?t=1698083574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Treacherous factions of zombies, hidden resources and untold stories are waiting to be discovered. Remember to stay vigilant for the sake of your village or risk being consumed by the untold horrors that await in EndZ Village.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/9d17c5b99957a71f612e17cbab5934d6.avif?t=1698083574\" width=620 height=182 /></span><br><br>-Zombie Age simulation<br>-Village construction<br>-Real-time survival engine<br>-Multiple types of zombies<br>-Variety of weapons to build and use<br>-Beautiful 2D graphics and animation<br><br>-Prevent attacks from zombies during village development<br>-Build weapons to increase attack power and defense<br>-Manage resources with farming<br>-Search for resources<br>-Produce meat with animal husbandry<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999190/extras/6ca06cdfa6fdcdb4a50551bb235821c6.avif?t=1698083574\" width=620 height=280 /></span>",
